author: rombert
msg: SLING-3764 - Incorrect resource processing order - directory artifact
- make sorting child nodes a separate command/step when processing
updates. This ensures that that the sorting is done at the end, when all
potential child node changes have been processed
- ensure that the resources returned from the SlingContentModuleFactory
are returned in a consistent order which allows us to process them in a
natural order form a vault serialization point of view
